OL,3,CFamily 'broken apart' by rise in short
OL,4,Cterm lets and holiday homes in town
OL,6,FGregg Easteal finds out how Whitby
OL,7,Fresidents have been affected by a rise
OL,8,Fin second homes, short-term lets and
OL,9,Fholiday homes
OL,11,FA woman from Whitby says her family is
OL,12,Fbeing broken apart by the struggle to
OL,13,Fbuy a home in the town.
OL,15,FShelly Nicholson has blamed the rise
OL,16,Fof holiday homes for the issue which
OL,17,Fshe believes is forcing out people who
OL,18,Fhave lived in the area for generations.
