OL,6,F"Mr brother is Whitby born and bred
OL,7,Fbut has had to move to as he couldn't
OL,8,Fafford to be on the housing market
OL,9,Fhere," she explained.
OL,11,F"My youngest son, 31, can't afford to
OL,12,Fbe on the housing market here. He's
OL,13,Fhad to move to Leicester for work and
OL,14,Fhousing.
OL,16,F"Any new housing estate, they're being
OL,17,Fbought up as second homes, holiday
OL,18,Flets, even on the council estates now
OL,19,Fthere's properties being brought up.
