OL,6,F"Our generations, we're losing that
OL,7,Fhistory."
OL,9,FMs Nicholson's words come as a new
OL,10,Fproposal to regulate short-term lets
OL,11,Fand holiday homes has been revealed by
OL,12,Fthe government in the hope of making
OL,13,Fit easier for people in tourist towns
OL,14,Fto remain in their communities.
OL,16,FDouglas Hill is an artist in who says
OL,17,Fhalf the houses in the street where he
OL,18,Flives are holiday homes.
OL,20,F"Everything that turns up is a second
OL,21,Fhome or a holiday home," he said.
