OL,6,FHe previously said he lived in St Ives
OL,7,Fin Cornwall "which went exactly the
OL,8,Fsame way", adding: "They're taking the
OL,9,Fparking, the noise, all the buildings
OL,10,Fare empty."
OL,12,FTheir comments to ITV Tyne Tees
OL,13,Fcoincided with Michael Gove, the
OL,14,FSecretary of State for Levelling Up,
OL,15,FHousing and Communities, announcing on
OL,16,FMonday 19 February that it was taking
OL,17,Fsteps to ensure that local people have
OL,18,Fgreater opportunities to buy homes.
