OL,3,CFamily 'broken apart' by rise in short
OL,4,Cterm lets and holiday homes in town
OL,6,FSpeaking in Cornwall, Mr Gove said:
OL,7,F"We know that short-term lets can be
OL,8,Fhelpful for the tourist economy, but
OL,9,Fwe also know there needs to be an
OL,10,Felement of control so that local
OL,11,Fpeople can also rent those homes as
OL,12,Fwell."
OL,14,FThe new measures include making future
OL,15,Fshort-term lets require planning
OL,16,Fpermission and joining a mandatory
OL,17,Fnational register.
