OL,6,FIt is hoped the move will give
OL,7,Fcommunities like Whitby greater
OL,8,Fcontrol of the number of holiday homes
OL,9,Fin their area.
OL,11,FCouncillor Phil Trumper said: "We're
OL,12,Fdefinitely going in the right
OL,13,Fdirection.
OL,15,F"We're looking at a town now where 20%
OL,16,Fof the housing stock is taken up by
OL,17,Fholiday lets and second homes.
