OL,6,F"That has a detrimental effect on
OL,7,Fyoung local people trying to get on
OL,8,Fthe ladder and trying to find a home
OL,9,Fthemselves. "
OL,11,FSpeaking following the announcement,
OL,12,FRachael Maskell, Labour MP for
OL,13,FCentral, said: "We've seen it in the
OL,14,FLake District, in Whitby and of course
OL,15,Fin York.
